 Calculate the total number of bolts of blue fiber.
\[
\begin{align*}
\text{Total blue fiber} &= \text{Number of blue bolts} \\
&= \frac{1}{2} \times \text{Total white fiber bolts} \\
&= \frac{1}{2} \times 4 \\
&= 2
\end{align*}
\]

Therefore, the correct answer is: \boxed{2}

